title: Joe De Sena - Spartan Race CEO
itunes:title: Joe De Sena - Spartan Race CEO
description:
Everyone likes to talk about the glam of the entrepreneur lifestyle, but they don’t talk about all the problems and responsibilities that come with it.
 
It takes a special kind of person to do this and have real success.
 
Joe De Sena is the CEO and founder of Spartan and the Death Race. He is also a NY Times best selling author of Spartan Up, Spartan Fit and The Spartan Way.
 
In this interview, we talk about what building a real business looks like and what kind of character you have to develop to win.
 
Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/joe-de-sena/
